title: BMW Standard Tools 2.10.0
description:
BMW Standard Tools v2.10.0

Includes:
EDIABAS 7.2.0
WINKFP 5.2.1
NFS 5.2.0
INPA 5.0.2.0
NCS Expert 1.0.0.1

This software should generally work on most BMW cars up to 2015 but I have only tested the software up to 2011.


Software Requirements:
32-bit Windows XP (32-bit Windows 7 will work if you run the installer in compatibility mode)

Hardware Requirements:
DCAN or K+DCAN cable USB to serial that you can find all over the internet

Additional Requirements:
This is simply the software for talking to the ECU. You will also need additional data files called "SP-DATEN" for communicating with the ECU. These will depend on your car and year. There are plenty of other torrents and websites describing this.


Good luck!!
